# Run Playwright Test

## Purpose

This skill helps create, maintain, and execute Playwright automated tests using TypeScript, Page Object Model (POM), and GitHub Actions CI/CD.

Use this skill when:

* Creating Playwright test cases
* Building Page Object Models
* Adding UI/UX validation tests
* Implementing functional testing
* Adding negative and boundary test scenarios
* Configuring GitHub Actions workflows
* Troubleshooting Playwright automation issues
* Improving test maintainability and stability

---

## Environment Requirements

### Install Dependencies

```bash
npm ci
```

### Install Playwright Browsers

```bash
npx playwright install --with-deps
```

