## Project Standards

### Technology Stack

* Playwright
* TypeScript
* GitHub Actions
* Page Object Model (POM)

### Coding Standards

* Use TypeScript strict mode
* Use Page Object Model
* Separate test logic from page logic
* Use meaningful test names
* Use `test.describe()`
* Use `test.step()`
* Avoid hard-coded waits (`sleep`)
* Use Playwright auto-waiting mechanisms

