## Test Coverage Requirements

Every feature should include:

### Positive Tests

* Happy Path validation
* Navigation verification
* Data validation
* UI element verification

### Negative Tests

* Invalid input
* Empty input
* Unauthorized access
* Error handling

### Boundary Tests

* Maximum length
* Minimum length
* Special characters
* Edge conditions

